Package: l1rotation
Title: Identify Individual Loading Vectors under Sparsity in Factor Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Simon", "Freyaldenhoven", , "simon.freyaldenhoven@phil.frb.org", role = c("aut", "cph")),
    person("Ryan", "Kobler", , "kobleary@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Estimate loading vectors using the l1 criterion as proposed in Freyaldenhoven (2025) <https://simonfreyaldenhoven.github.io/papers/factor_rotation.pdf>. Given a data matrix, find the rotation of the loading matrix with the smallest l1-norm and/or test for the presence of local factors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
