    doParallel,
    dplyr,
    foreach,
    ggplot2,
    magrittr,
    matrixStats,
    pracma,
    scales,
    stats,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    tidyselect
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
